reviewText: This briefly examines the practice of child labor around the world which is often caused by the sever poverty of the places where it occurs, heartbreaking. Essentially slavery/exploitation. Vocations include young fisher boys, picking in dumps, run-a-way teen girls providing physical companionship for truckers, and child soldier. Insightful and sickening as adults are responsible.
Incredible film that really puts the human face on the issue of Human Trafficking. These images will stay with you long after the film ends.
